#include <vector>
#include <string>
#include <algorithm>
using namespace std;

int main() {
    int n;
    cin >> n;
    vector<vector<int>> board(n, vector<int>(n));
    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
            cin >> board[i][j];
        }
    }
    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
            if (board[i][j] == 2) {
                board[i][j] = 1;
            } else if (board[i][j] == 1) {
                board[i][j] = 0;
            }
        }
    }
    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
            cout << board[i][j];
        }
        cout << endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
